      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"invitation\" sounds so peaceful, honestly. It's just that they do so much for me... the doctors, the cleaning, the driving. I look at them and I just see how much of their lives they're spending on me. It feels selfish to keep dragging it out when I'm not really \"living\" anymore, just existing.",
